caller_intent: The caller wants to transfer an existing motorcycle insurance policy to a different motorcycle and confirm whether the current policy was canceled.
resolution_steps: Agent asked for the caller's name and policy details.
Agent checked the system and confirmed an active motorcycle policy under William Sterling Jr.
Agent offered to transfer the policy to a different motorcycle.
Agent initiated a transfer to a dedicated insurance agent to handle the request.
summary: Caller requested to transfer an active motorcycle insurance policy to a new motorcycle. The agent confirmed the policy's status and transferred the call to an agent for further processing. The call ended with the agent agreeing to handle the transfer.
